'''Doolis''' was a major [[City/Legends|city]] on [[Caprioril]].<ref name="CSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref> It was home to the [[Doolis Podrace Arena]] before it was shut down after [[Podracing/Legends|podracing]] was banned on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]].<ref name="HNN45">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|45|sports/13228_2.html|Podracing Banned on Caprioril}}</ref>

